        recognize your browser when you next visit the site.</p>

    <p>You can configure your browser to inform you about the
        use of cookies so that you can decide on a case-by-case basis whether to accept or reject a cookie. Alternatively,
        your browser can be configured to automatically accept cookies under certain conditions or to always reject them, or
        to automatically delete cookies when closing your browser. Disabling cookies may limit the functionality of this
        website.</p>

    <p>Cookies which are necessary to allow electronic communications or to provide certain functions you
        wish to use (such as the shopping cart) are stored pursuant to Art. 6 paragraph 1, letter f of DSGVO. The website
        operator has a legitimate interest in the storage of cookies to ensure an optimized service provided free of
        technical errors. If other cookies (such as those used to analyze your surfing behavior) are also stored, they will
        be treated separately in this privacy policy.</p>

